<font size="4">I was able to associate user's message <em><%= @message.body %></em> with this intent:</font>
<br />
<font size="5"><%= @intent.name %></font>
<br /><br />
<font size="4">The most appropriate answer to this message might be:</font> <font size="5"><em><%= link_to "#{@top_answer.reply}", answer_path(@top_answer) %></em></font>.
